\f0 \
\
2) You can assign and keep track of rewards 
\f2 \uc0\u55356 \u57217 
\f0  for the child. For example, after 3 successful potties, give her an ice cream cone 
\f2 \uc0\u55356 \u57190 
\f0 . \
\
